'''Peace TV'''是一家总部位于[[阿联酋|阿联酋]][[迪拜|迪拜]]的的[[非營利組織|非盈利性]][[卫星电视|卫星电视台]]，由[[印度|印度]][[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]学者[[扎基尔·奈克|扎基尔·奈克]]（{{lang-en|Zakir Naik}}）创办。该台使用[[英语|英语]]、[[乌尔都语|乌尔都语]]、[[孟加拉语|孟加拉语]]和[[汉语普通话|汉语普通话]]广播，每天24小时免费播出。节目以宣传伊斯兰教教义为主。

该台于2006年1月21日开播，起初仅有一个英语频道<ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.ohmynews.com/articleview/article_view.asp?no=360555&rel_no=1 |title=Does 'Peace TV' Encourage Interfaith Amity? |work=[[OhMyNews|OhMyNews]] |date=2007-05-10 |author=Aataai Gazi Mahbub |accessdate=2015-10-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070525224202/http://english.ohmynews.com/articleview/article_view.asp?no=360555&rel_no=1 |archivedate=2007-05-25 }}</ref>。2009年6月，乌尔都语频道开播；2011年4月22日，孟加拉语频道开播<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.peacetvbangla.com/about_peacetv.htm |title=Welcome to Peace TV Bangla |publisher=Peacetvbangla.com |date= |accessdate=2015-10-28 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202235409/http://www.peacetvbangla.com/about_peacetv.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年10月，Peace TV汉语普通话频道开播<ref>{{YouTube|n-prS2h_J30|PEACE TV CHINESE-MANDARIN Launched on ASIASAT-7}}</ref>。

==概况==
据创办人扎基尔·奈克称，Peace TV是一个“{{le|寓教于乐|edutainment|}}（{{lang-en|edutainment}}）”的电视台<ref>{{Cite news |title=British authorities consider banning Peace TV |newspaper=The Express Tribune |location=Pakistan |date=2010-11-30 |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/121553/extremist-message-british-authorities-consider-banning-peace-tv/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110223172424/http://tribune.com.pk/story/121553/extremist-message-british-authorities-consider-banning-peace-tv/ |accessdate=2015-10-28 |archivedate=2011-02-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，节目包括直播、演讲及儿童教育等方面<ref>{{cite web | title = An Inter - Religious dialogue for Spiritual Enlightenment | work = The True Call | date = 2006-12-13 | url = http://www.thetruecall.com/home/modules.php?name=News&file=article&sid=167 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102191816/http://www.thetruecall.com/home/modules.php?name=News&file=article&sid=167 | accessdate = 2015-10-28 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。该台通过卫星覆盖全世界200多个国家和地区<ref>{{cite web |url=http://peacetv.in/about_peace_tv.html |title=About Peace TV |publisher=Peacetv.in |accessdate=2013-11-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131126015816/http://peacetv.in/about_peace_tv.html |archivedate=2013-11-26 }}</ref>，同时通过[[Livestation|Livestation]]在网上免费播出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://peacetv.tv/en-gb/schedules/#pageTop |title=Schedules |publisher=Peacetv.tv |date= |accessdate=2015-10-28 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203003954/http://peacetv.tv/en-gb/schedules/#pageTop |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，该台也在[[美国|美国]]多个城市通过[[地面电视|地面电视]]播出。扎基尔·奈克所拥有的“伊斯兰研究基金会”（{{lang-en|Islamic Research Foundation}}）对该台进行资助，2009年的资助额为125万[[英镑|英镑]]<ref name="standard1">{{cite news |author=Harper, Tom |title=Banned hate preacher still broadcasting after 'Jews are enemy of Islam' claim |newspaper=London Evening Standard |date=2011-02-11 |url=http://www.standard.co.uk/news/banned-hate-preacher-still-broadcasting-after-jews-are-enemy-of-islam-claim-6566248.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216020622/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/banned-hate-preacher-still-broadcasting-after-jews-are-enemy-of-islam-claim-6566248.html |archivedate=2013-12-16 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-10-28 }}</ref>。

