*Peace TV Albanian：[[阿尔巴尼亚语|阿尔巴尼亚语]]频道（2013年停播）

==争议==
2011年，英国[[通讯管理局|通讯管理局]]（{{lang-en|Office of Communications}}）在对Peace TV进行调查后，指控其宣扬极端思想。该台曾声称[[911事件|911事件]]是美国人“自导自演”，并被指宣传[[反犹主义|反犹主义]]<ref name="standard1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/cleric-who-claimed-every-muslim-should-be-a-terrorist-and-blames-george-bush-for-911-given-10080539.html|title=Cleric who claimed 'every Muslim should be a terrorist' and blames George Bush for 9/11 given prestigious award by Saudi Arabia|publisher=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|author=Jamie Campbell|accessdate=2015-10-28|date=2015-03-02|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127225814/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/cleric-who-claimed-every-muslim-should-be-a-terrorist-and-blames-george-bush-for-911-given-10080539.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而次年该台又因为在节目中宣称“[[叛教_(伊斯蘭教)|背叛伊斯兰教]]的人都该被处死”而被英国通讯事务办公室裁定为违规<ref name="tele1">{{Cite news |author=Barrett, David |title=Preachers of hate on British TV: what they said that broke the broadcasting rules |newspaper=[[每日电讯报|The Telegraph]] |date=2013-02-09 |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/9859822/Preachers-of-hate-on-British-TV-what-they-said-that-broke-the-broadcasting-rules.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6az3ouUnV?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/9859822/Preachers-of-hate-on-British-TV-what-they-said-that-broke-the-broadcasting-rules.html |archivedate=2015-08-22 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-10-28 }}</ref>。

2012年，包括Peace TV在内共计二十余家电视台在印度被禁播，印度政府方面称，该台大量播放反印内容，并宣布任何提供这些电视台信号的[[有线电视|有线电视]]业者都将面临处罚<ref>{{Cite news|author=Sharma, Pratul|title=Government puts 24 foreign 'hate channels' on notice for showing anti-India TV shows after intelligence alert|newspaper=The Daily Mail|date=2012-12-05|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/indiahome/indianews/article-2243584/Government-puts-24-foreign-hate-channels-notice-showing-anti-India-TV-shows-intelligence-alert.html|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121209041619/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/indiahome/indianews/article-2243584/Government-puts-24-foreign-hate-channels-notice-showing-anti-India-TV-shows-intelligence-alert.html|archivedate=2012-12-09|deadurl=no|accessdate=2015-10-28}}</ref>。

对于外界的批评，Peace TV称，他们只是在阐释《[[古兰经|古兰经]]》的教义<ref name="tele1"/>。创始人扎基尔·奈克对该台被印度政府禁播感到不满，并希望禁令能够解除<ref>{{cite news |author=Hassan, Rashid |date=2014-07-06 |title=Ban on Peace TV will be lifted soon: Zakir Naik |url=http://www.arabnews.com/news/597351 |agency=Arab News |publisher=Arab News |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706045220/http://www.arabnews.com/news/597351 |archivedate=2014-07-06 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-10-28 }}</ref>。

